description: "Endangered Species" concludes! As Gus lies dying, he has a new and terrible vision that will test the group's faith. Meanwhile, Lucy and Jepperd's relationship crumbles, and Walter Fish is left to pick up the pieces.
name: Endangered Species: Part Five

description: In "Knuckle Up" part 1 of 5, it's war on the reservation as Red Crow loses his grip on the reins, Agent Nitz gains momentum and Dash Bad Horse faces his toughest foe yet.
name: Knuckle Up, Part One of Five

description: Started as a challenge from a girl to an unwanted suitor , the search for the true origin of the jokes turns into a tragic adventure that comes to cost human lives . Even Martin Mystere is called into play and, in the Nevada desert , he discovers a shocking truth : the jokes that, for centuries , passed from mouth to mouth, overcoming political and linguistic borders , are part of a plan to condition the will of men !
name: L'uomo che inventava le barzellette

description: Martin Mystere, Diana and Java are in China for a visit of one of the archaeological wonders of the world: " the Terracotta Army ", more than six thousand life-size statues, built in the third century BC by Emperor Huang Chin in defense of his grave. Here, our heroes are involved in a fight to the death, that seems to have at stake the domain of China itself .
name: Intrigo a Pechino

description: It is in place a complex plot involving the Chinese government , a young Japanese, a group of mercenaries trained in South Korea , a powerful multinational corporation , a mysterious woman who lives in an inaccessible fortress and , of course , Martin Mystere , which will disrupt a mad plan of conquest . Then , the Detective of the Impossible is to investigate a series of fierce and inexplicable murders occurred in the border region between California and Mexico ...
name: L'esercito di terracotta
La cosa da un altro mondo
